The '''Institute of Business Administration''' was established in 2000 as a private institute for business and commerce studies. It became the '''College of Business Administration''' '''(CBA)''' in 2003. It is now known as the University of Business and Technology.
== About == The objectives ate given in <ref name="cba.edu">[http://www.cba.edu.sa/objectives.aspx?pageId=2] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101207060938/http://www.cba.edu.sa/objectives.aspx?pageId=2 |date=7 December 2010 }}</ref>
=== Accreditation === CBA is accredited by the Saudi Ministry of Higher Education.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mohe.gov.sa/en/studyinside/privateedu/Pages/Colleges.aspx|title=Private Colleges|publisher=MOHE|date=17 October 2011|accessdate=26 March 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805080130/http://www.mohe.gov.sa/en/studyinside/privateedu/Pages/Colleges.aspx|archivedate=5 August 2012|df=dmy-all}}</ref> In June 2012, UBT was awarded the National Accreditation NCAAA (National Commission for Academic Accreditation and Assessment). <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/CBAJeddahCampus/posts/252173294897970|title=Congrats UBT / CBA!|publisher=Facebook|date=6 July 2012|accessdate=26 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=صحيفة عكاظ |url=http://www.okaz.com.sa/new/Issues/20120701/Con20120701514008.htm#.T_APHQR7kmM.facebook|title=صحيفة عكاظ- شؤون الوطن - بأمر الملك: جامعة للتكنولوجيا بجدة و9 كليات جديدة |newspaper=Okaz|date=30 June 2012|accessdate=26 March 2013}}</ref> CBA is the first private college in Saudi Arabia that is working towards the Institutional and Programs accreditation from the NCAAA for the period May 2010 to May 2014 for the following five programs: * Accounting * Finance * Human Resource * Marketing * Management Information System
CBA did not apply for accrediting supply chain management program since "the students had not graduated from the program yet", as announced by Dr. Abdullah Dahlan (board of trustees, chairman).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=267807873327028&set=a.124711997636617.25140.124688357638981&type=1|title=Timeline Photos|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=26 March 2013}}</ref>
